---
title: Tex-Mex Turkey Bowls with Guacamole and Feta
description: Tonight, tuck into this bowl of punchy Mexican-inspired flavours! Turkey gets boosted by salsa and our Enchilada Spice Blend, while rice gets sautéed with bell peppers to give it a subtle sweetness. A dollop of ready-to-eat guac brings loads of flavour with little effort in the kitchen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-dinde-tex-mex-c5a7f3c7.jpg
